All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,Token>
public class TokenIndex
extends java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,Token>

The InvertedIndex class. Holds all the words that have been parsed from the documents in the scanner. It extends the HashMap class and holds the words as a key-value pair: where the LinkedList is the listing of the documentIDs in which the word appears
